Description: Morse Micro 802.11ah (Wi-Fi HaLow) wireless driver - DKMS source
 Out-of-tree kernel driver for Morse Micro Wi-Fi HaLow (802.11ah) wireless
 chipsets, including MM6108 and MM8108. This is the Gateworks fork with
 additional kernel compatibility fixes.
 .
 The driver supports SDIO, SPI, and USB bus transports. It requires firmware
 files from the morse-firmware package to be installed in /lib/firmware/morse/.
 .
 This package provides the source code for the morse kernel modules and uses
 DKMS to automatically build them for each installed kernel version.
